<p>On 10/18/20██ the following unauthorized modifications to the experimental data of <a href="/scp-2719">SCP-2719</a> were logged by the external monitoring server. Based on the information gained from the logs, and the successful recovery of Site-81, Dr. Watkins has been given a posthumous commendation.</p>
